title: Cocksucker Blues 1972   Rolling Stones
description:
A film by photographer Robert Frank on the Rolling Stone's 1972 American tour. Not released by the Stones... 

Trivia: The Rolling Stones were upset by this film's portrayal of them and sued to prevent its release. The film is under a court order that only allows it to be shown once a year with director Robert Frank present in person. 

Genre: semi documentary / Music
 
VHS rip to DVD / Simpel menu/ no extras/ no subs/
